<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EJS 2</title>
</head>

<h1>EJS, example 2</h1>

<p>This page serves two purposes:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Show you you can use Node.js and EJS templating without a database</li>
    <li>Show you how the value of a Node.js variable can be added directly to a page.</li>
</ul>

<body>
    <div>
        <h3>For your information...</h3>
        <dl>
            <dt>__dirname</dt>
            <dd><%= node.dirname %></dd>
        </dl>
        <dl>
            <dt>__filename</dt>
            <dd><%= node.filename %></dd>
        </dl>
    </div>
</body>
</html>